snippet.textDisplay: What bothered me about the parents in this episode is that the mother said they wanted Gordon to tell their daughter what they didn't want to tell her, because they were in a personal, as well as business relationship. What if they didn't get on "Kitchen Nightmares"? I don't think they would have let the restaurant close, because they couldn't criticize their daughter. You have to tell people close to you the harsh truth, sometimes.
